# https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/blob/master/GUIDE.md#configuration-file

### Don't let ripgrep vomit really long lines to my terminal.
--max-columns=150

### Flag below means: --no-ignore --hidden --binary
-uuu

### Display hidden files
--hidden

### Ignore binary files
--no-binary

### Ignore directories
--glob=!.git/
--glob=!.angular/
--glob=!node_modules/
